page.title: 10GARAGES AND TRANSPORT
page.content: In a traffic count from 12.05 till 12.35 we found the most popular make of cars was Vauxhall,then came Ford ,British Leyland and Datsun.For vans and lorries Ford was the most popular with Vauxhall/ Bedford close behind. Cars driving in the direction of Carnock came up the road every three minutes because of the traffic lights just down the road. There are lots of private coach companys such as Jacks,Allisons,Alexanders,Rennies and Greyhound Coaches.All of these companys are based in and around Dunfermline.Curtis Motors is the main Vauxhall dealer in the area selling new and used cars.Norman Rollo Motors is also based in Dunfermline selling new and used Volvo cars.
